&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a full time Band 3 Administration Support Worker on a fixed term contract from October 2020 to March 2021. This post is currently based at Chy Trevail, Bodmin, and will involve working on a rota over 7 days a week and does include evenings and weekends. The post holder is required to be flexible with opportunities to work from home over weekends and with future discussions over places based care in Primary Care Networks. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role of the Administration Support Worker is to work alongside prioritisers who are Nurses, Social Workers, and Therapists processing and managing the flow of patient referrals through the CCC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
